text: 486 Squadron or 486th Squadron may refer to: * No. 486 Squadron RAAF, Australia * No. 486 Squadron RNZAF, a New Zealand fighter unit of the Royal Air Force that served in Europe during World War II * 486th Aero Squadron, Air Service, United States Army * 486th Bombardment Squadron, United States Army Air Forces and United States Air Force * 486th Fighter Squadron, United States Army Air Forces * 486th Flight Test Squadron, United States Air Force
title: 486 Squadron
